The heart shadow is not large, the coronary artery is calcified, the morphology of large vessels is normal, and multiple small lymph nodes are seen in the mediastinum and bilateral armpits. A small amount of pleural effusion on the left side.

impression: Right pneumonia. Two emphysema with interstitial changes. Bilateral bronchial arteries dilated and moved. Low density focus of thyroid.
finding: After radiotherapy and chemotherapy for small cell carcinoma of the right lung, irregular soft tissue density shadow can be seen at the right hilum of the lung, with unclear boundary, surrounding the right hilum of the lung, with a large section of about 2.0 × 2.7 cm, moderate enhancement on enhanced scan; The markings of the remaining lungs are increased and disordered, and locally interweave into a network. Multiple irregular light transmission areas are seen between them. Slightly high-density fuzzy shadows are seen in the upper and lower lobes of the right lung, and the left pulmonary hilum is not large. Slightly large lymph nodes can be seen in the mediastinum. The shape of heart shadow and large vessels is normal. The bronchial arteries on both sides are dilated and tortuous. Pleural thickening on both sides, no obvious signs of pleural effusion on both sides. Low density foci are seen in the thyroid gland.

impression: Bilateral pulmonary nodules. Interstitial changes in both lungs. Low density lesions in pancreas.
finding: Thorax is symmetrical, bilateral lung markings are increased and disordered, multiple nodules can be seen in both lung fields, the maximum is about 0.6 × 0.5cm。 The shape of heart shadow and heart big vessels is normal, and no obvious mass or enlarged lymph node is found in mediastinum. No pleural effusion or pleural thickening. A round low density lesion was found in the pancreas.
